    "Author": "VladislavSolyannikov",
    "Comment": "TechArt comment: \nWarpSlash Overdrive: sequential jump-attack chain via CustomAbilityQueue.\nFlow: 1) MarkTargets applies TargetMarker to all enemies in radius 4 (snapshot), 2) pick random enemy with TargetMarker but no HitMarker, 3) JumpAttack with WarpSlashJumpAugment animation + LandAttack on landing (applies HitMarker), 4) repeat until all marked enemies hit.\nTarget snapshot ensures only enemies in original radius are attacked, even as unit moves.\nUses ContextConditionHasBuffFromCaster so multiple units can overdrive independently.\nSub-blueprints: MarkTargets (d7e8f9a0), JumpAttack (99387c88), LandAttack (799dae4d), QueueContinue (512dc13c), HitMarker (a3b7d92e), TargetMarker (b4c8e03f).",
